objects.name: weather_data
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE weather_data (
    Date_Time TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    TempC INTEGER,
    DewPoint INTEGER,
    Rel_Hum INTEGER,
    PresskPa INTEGER,
    Weather TEXT,
    PM1_0 INTEGER,
    PM2_5 INTEGER,
    PM4 INTEGER,
    PM10 INTEGER
)

objects.name: weather_prediction
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE weather_prediction (
    Date TEXT,
    Time TEXT,
    Temperature REAL
)
